description: Gets the list of annotations for a component for given time range

start.description: The start time to query from for annotations, cannot be older than 90 days from current date.

end.description: The end time to query for annotations.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group. The name is case insensitive.

api_version.description: The API version to use for this operation.

subscription_id.description: The ID of the target subscription.

resource_name.description: The name of the Application Insights component resource.
